00:13:55.190 --> 00:14:00.370
The, if the Hebrew data is off by a
day from the English date it means

00:14:00.370 --> 00:14:03.820
that they died after dark,
on that English date.

00:14:03.820 --> 00:14:08.610
So that sometimes gives you a
useful piece of family history,

00:14:08.610 --> 00:14:11.440 position:56%
