00:14:28.160 --> 00:14:34.390
Turned out, that the stone cutters
had cut the date of the unveiling

00:14:34.390 --> 00:14:37.620
of the stone in the English date.

00:14:37.620 --> 00:14:39.760
And the Hebrew date was
the correct date of death.

00:14:39.760 --> 00:14:44.320
I only found that out
by doing some research,

00:14:44.320 --> 00:14:50.600 position:56%
